&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;CAPSJ Consulting Limited is seeking a&amp;nbsp;senior&amp;nbsp;leader with an active&amp;nbsp;defence or security-sector&amp;nbsp;background to serve as SVP. Reporting to Tiree Inc. and Canderel Group senior management, the SVP will lead CAPSJ’s delivery operations — the core of the business — and assume full accountability for business performance, growth, and the firm’s standing within Canada’s federal defence procurement ecosystem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:60,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:80}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
