&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The SVP provides senior leadership across all aspects of CAPSJ’s day-to-day operations, with direct accountability for delivery quality, team performance, and client satisfaction inside&amp;nbsp;some of&amp;nbsp;Canada’s most regulated project environments. This includes working across relevant&amp;nbsp;government and&amp;nbsp;institutional portfolios and in close coordination with project&amp;nbsp;groups, construction managers, and technical security stakeholders to ensure aligned, disciplined delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
